testsuite.name: com.tim.one.service.ProjectTransactionServiceIntegrationSpec

testcase.name: When we have a costs with 5% and 10% and a project budget 600, we expect that project has a CRE 615
When we have a costs with 12% and 16% and a project budget 10100, we expect that project has a CRE 10128
When we have a costs with 5% and 10% and units with quantities 1, 3, 5 and budget with 500, we expect that project has a TRI 0.6277777778
When we have a costs with 12% and 16% and units with quantities 2, 4, 6 and budget with 1000, we expect that project has a TRI 0.3866666667
When we have a costs with 5% and 10% and units with quantities 1, 3, 5 and budget with 500, we expect that project has a TRF 3.1388888890
When we have a costs with 12% and 16% and units with quantities 2, 4, 6 and budget with 1000, we expect that project has a TRF 1.1600000001
